(9, '2010-04-07 08:04:15', '2010-04-07 08:18:28', NULL, 'Privacy Policy', '<div class="clearfix static-page-block">\r\n<h3>Terms</h3>\r\n<div class="clearfix"><dl class="faq-list"><dt>Groupon is an intermediary service offering discounts through primary vendors. We do our very best to insure that you have an optimum experience with your Groupon certificate from purchase to redemption.</dt><dd>Should there be a problem with, or question about your purchase, please contact us as soon as possible.</dd><dt>In certain circumstances, Groupon certificates may be returned for the full purchase price.</dt><dd>Examples of these situations include, but are not limited to:</dd><dt>The business closes prior to expiration of Groupon certificate, or a legitimate discrepancy in our printed terms (i.e. expiration dates, location of vendor)</dt><dd>If you wish to inquire about returning a Groupon certificate for a refund, please email us at <a href="mailto:help@groupon.com">help@groupon.com</a> Your happiness is our success.</dd></dl></div>\r\n<h3>Your Privacy</h3>\r\n<div class="clearfix"><dt>All credit card information is encrypted for your security and card information is deleted within 48 hours of your purchase. Information provided to Groupon will be used solely for the purpose of conducting business with Groupon.</dt></div>\r\n</div>', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, '', NULL, 'privacy_policy', 0),
(2, '2009-07-11 11:16:54', '2010-05-26 11:05:43', NULL, 'About', '<div class="static-block">\r\n<p>##SITE_NAME## began when an independent business-owner had a eureka moment. - the best way to grow your business is to give your customers and clients something exciting to talk about.</p>\r\n<p>##SITE_NAME## gives visitors to our site the opportunity to do a lot of talking. We offer one huge discount every day for a carefully selected mix of dining establishments, spas, salons, and more.</p>\r\n<p>We work with both new and established vendors. So, on Tuesday, you can try the Fiery Dragon Rolls at the new sushi place in Midtown and by Friday, you can say goodbye to the work week at the Decatur pub where everybody knows your name all for less.</p>\r\n<p class="spacer">##SITE_NAME## is able to offer these dazzling discounts because there is power in numbers. Business owners don''t mind giving a discounted rate if it means seeing lots of new faces (or familiar faces more often).</p>\r\n<p class="spacer">We love what we do and so do our customers</p>\r\n</div>', 'about.ctp', 0, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 'about', 0),
