(6, '2009-07-17 07:55:38', '2010-04-07 07:48:58', NULL, 'FAQ', '<div class="main-center-block">\r\n<div class="clearfix static-page-block">\r\n<h3>What is ##SITE_NAME##?</h3>\r\n<p>Each day, ##SITE_NAME## features an unbeatable deal on the best stuff to do, see, eat, and buy in your city. By promising businesses a minimum number of customers, we get discounts you would not find anywhere else. We call it "collective buying power!"</p>\r\n<h3>Do I have to sign up a group of people I know to get the deal?</h3>\r\n<p>Nope - our hundreds of thousands of members make up a big enough group. You will probably want to invite people anyway, though - ##SITE_NAME## are fun to use with friends, grandparents, and men who wear monocles.</p>\r\n<h3>I like todays deal - how do I get it?</h3>\r\n<p>Just click "BUY" before the offer ends at midnight. If the minimum number of people sign up, we will charge your card and send you a link to print your ##SITE_NAME##. If not enough people join, no one gets it (and you would not be charged), so invite your friends to make sure you get the deal!</p>\r\n<h3>What happens if the ##SITE_NAME## does not reach its required minimum number of purchasers?</h3>\r\n<p>If not enough people sign up, then the deal is canceled, and you would not be charged. Better luck next time! So if you really want the ##SITE_NAME##, be sure to either beg or threaten your friends .</p>\r\n<h3>Do I need to use my ##SITE_NAME## the same day I buy it?</h3>\r\n<p>No. Many ##SITE_NAME## have an expiration date, but you never have to use them on the date of purchase.</p>\r\n<h3>I bought a ##SITE_NAME## - how do I use it?</h3>\r\n<p>Once you are charged, you will receive an email with a link to sign in and print your ##SITE_NAME##. The ##SITE_NAME## has redemption instructions and a map right on it!</p>\r\n<h3>Can I buy a ##SITE_NAME## as a gift for someone else?</h3>\r\n<p>Yes. We communicate with all the businesses that we work with that ##SITE_NAME##s can be gifted, and unless the Fine Print specifically states otherwise, gift away! To have us send them the gift, select the gift option at checkout.</p>\r\n<h3>Wait, my name is on the ##SITE_NAME##. Are you sure I can use this as a gift?</h3>\r\n<p>Yes!</p>\r\n<h3>If I do not use the full value of the ##SITE_NAME## in one visit, can I use the remainder later?</h3>\r\n<p>No. Unless otherwise stated you do not receive store credit or cash back for whatever you do not use. Bring a friend - share a little!</p>\r\n<h3>Can I combine my ##SITE_NAME## with other offers or specials?</h3>\r\n<p>No... not unless the ##SITE_NAME## specifically states otherwise.</p>\r\n<h3>Am I billed as soon as I join a ##SITE_NAME##?</h3>\r\n<p>No - you are only charged if the ##SITE_NAME## reaches the required minimum.</p>\r\n<h3>Is ##SITE_NAME## safe?</h3>\r\n<p>Extremely. Your credit card number is transmitted by SSL directly to a secure electronic vault. At no time is your credit card information stored on our servers.</p>\r\n<h3>Can I return a ##SITE_NAME##?</h3>\r\n<p>Read this, and then if you want, give us a call: (877) 788-7858.</p>\r\n<h3>Do you ever remove comments from the discussion board?</h3>\r\n<p>Generally, no. We only remove comments when someone is making personal attacks or engaging in other conventional forms of trolling.</p>\r\n<h3>What if the business for my ##SITE_NAME## closes down?</h3>\r\n<p>If anything happens that makes it impossible for you to redeem your ##SITE_NAME##, we will make sure you get your money back.</p>\r\n<h3>How can I get my business on ##SITE_NAME##?</h3>\r\n<p>Check out ##SITE_NAME## Works for more information</p>\r\n<h3>I just sent a referral to my friend - now what?</h3>\r\n<p>If your friend makes their first ##SITE_NAME## purchase within 72 hours from the time they click on the referral link you send them, we will send you an email to tell you that we have put $10 worth of credits in your account.</p>\r\n<h3>What if the person I refer subscribes to the site - any love for that?</h3>\r\n<p>Of course! If someone you refers subscribes within 72 hours, you will receive a $10 credit whenever they make their first purchase.</p>\r\n<h3>Can I refer as many people as I want?</h3>\r\n<p>Yes!</p>\r\n<h3>I received referral codes from three people - do they all get rewarded?</h3>\r\n<p>No, only the last code you click on before making your first purchase will generate a reward for the person who sent it to you. Which friend do you like best?</p>\r\n<h3>Why do you only feature one deal a day? I want more ##SITE_NAME##s!</h3>\r\n<p>When you are looking for stuff to do, choice can be overwhelming. We focus on one great thing each day and offer it at an unbeatable price to make things simple for you. Hang out with ##SITE_NAME## for a week, and you will find something that is impossible to refuse.</p>\r\n<h3>One of your write-ups stated that "hummingbirds come from cocoons"... I am not sure that is correct.</h3>\r\n<p>Thank you for your suggestion, but it is correct.</p>\r\n<h3>Where did you get the name "##SITE_NAME##?"</h3>\r\n<p>##SITE_NAME## is a city in Switzerland where Goodyear tires are sold at heavily discounted rates.</p>\r\n<h3>When will ##SITE_NAME## be in my city?</h3>\r\n<p>Hopefully soon - we are growing fast. If you had like to help us launch ##SITE_NAME## in your city, feel free to email us.</p>\r\n<h3>Who are you guys?</h3>\r\n<p>##SITE_NAME## evolved out of The Point, a platform for organizing not only group discounts, but all forms of collective action. You can learn more about ##SITE_NAME##, and learn more about The Point.</p>\r\n<h3>Where is ##SITE_NAME## based?</h3>\r\n<p>##SITE_NAME## is headquartered in Chicago. We also have employees in cities across the U.S.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '', 0, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 'faq', 0),
(7, '2009-07-21 15:56:45', '2009-07-21 15:56:45', NULL, 'Terms and conditions', '<p>By using ##SITE_NAME## you signify that you have read, understand and agree to be bound by these Terms and conditions.<br /><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ##SITE_NAME## is concerned about the safety and privacy of all its Users, especially children. Therefore, children under the age of 13 are not permitted to use ##SITE_NAME##<br /><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ##SITE_NAME## reserves the right to remove any image for any reason whatsoever. Specifically, any image uploaded that is pornographic or offensive in nature (including nudity, violence, sexual acts, or sexually provocative images.), infringes upon copyrights not held by the uploader, is illegal or violates any laws, will be immediately deleted and the IP address of the uploaded reported to authorities. Violating these terms will result result in termination of your ability to upload further images.<br /><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; We reserve the right to ban any individual uploader or website domain from using our servies for any reason.<br /><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; We cannot be held liable for any damages. All data, photographs, messages, graphics, comments, text, tags, or other materials ("Content"), are the sole responsibility of the person from whom such Content originated. You, and not ''.Configure::read(''site.name'').'', are entirely responsible for all Content that you upload, post, email, transmit or otherwise make available through ##SITE_NAME## does not control the Content posted and does not guarantee the accuracy or integrity of such Content.</p>', '', 0, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 'term-and-conditions', 0),
(10, '2010-05-05 12:12:23', '2010-05-05 12:35:56', NULL, 'Learn How ##SITE_NAME## Works', '<div class="content">\r\n<div class="page_content">\r\n<div class="how_it_works">\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>How It Works</h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Each day we feature something cool to do at an unbeatable price.</li>\r\n<li>You only get it if enough people join that day&hellip; so invite your friends!</li>\r\n<li>Check back the next day for another awesome ##SITE_NAME##!</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>Still have questions? <a href="##SITE_URL##page/faq">Check out the FAQ</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="border_spacer">\r\n<div class="page_content">\r\n<div class="groupon_for_businesses">\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>##SITE_NAME## for Businesses</h3>\r\n<p>With an unparalleled ability to drive hundreds &mdash; even thousands &mdash; of customers through your door, it''s no wonder that 95% of our surveyed business partners want to be featured on ##SITE_NAME## again.  Read more about getting featured on ##SITE_NAME##.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="border_spacer">\r\n<div class="page_content">\r\n<div class="about_groupon">\r\n<div class="copy">\r\n<h3>About ##SITE_NAME##</h3>\r\n<p>##SITE_NAME## started in November 2008 as part of The Point, a platform for collective action. We started ##SITE_NAME## to make it easier for people to enjoy the great things in their community.  We do it by offering daily deals at unbeatable prices through the power of group buying.</p>\r\n<p>We also use ##SITE_NAME##''s consumer collective to lift each community we touch, by featuring local charities and organizing support for community causes.</p>\r\n<p>We treat our customers the way that we like to be treated, and do everything we can to offer a "too good to be true" experience from the moment you buy your ##SITE_NAME## to the day you use it.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, '', NULL, 'learn', 0),
(11, '2010-05-05 14:37:51', '2010-05-25 12:26:22', NULL, 'What do you get with ##SITE_NAME## that you can’t get anywhere else?', '<h2>What do you get with ##SITE_NAME## that you can&rsquo;t get anywhere else?</h2>\r\n<table style="width: 681px; height: 640px;" border="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="background-image: url(http://grouponpro.dev.agriya.com/img/theme-image/bg_why/bg-why1.png); width: 389px; height: 290px;" valign="top">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="why-groupon-subtitle">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="why-groupon-subtitle">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="why-groupon-subtitle">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="why-groupon-subtitle">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="why-groupon-subtitle">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="why-groupon-subtitle"><strong><span style="color: #000000;">Valuable New Customers, Guaranteed</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #000000;">Since a minimum number of people must buy for the offer to be valid, ##SITE_NAME## guarantees paying customers. These subscribers are not looking for &ldquo;the perfect deal.&rdquo; They&rsquo;re looking for the perfect excuse to try something new. The average ##SITE_NAME## customer spends 60 percent more than the value of the ##SITE_NAME##.</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class="why-groupon-subtitle" style="width: 10px;">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style="background-image: url(http://grouponpro.dev.agriya.com/img/theme-image/bg_why/bg-why2.png); width: 389px; height: 290px;" valign="top">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="why-groupon-subtitle">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="why-groupon-subtitle">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="why-groupon-subtitle">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="why-groupon-subtitle">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="why-groupon-subtitle"><strong><span style="color: #000000;">Efficient, Measurable, Risk-Free Marketing</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #000000;">It costs nothing to be featured on ##SITE_NAME##. We make money by taking a piece of each ##SITE_NAME## we sell. In other words, we only win if you win &ndash; and you know what you&rsquo;re getting at every step of the process</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style="height: 50px;">\r\n<td style="height: 50px;">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style="width: 10px; height: 50px;">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style="height: 50px;">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="background-image: url(http://grouponpro.dev.agriya.com/img/theme-image/bg_why/bg-why3.png); width: 389px; height: 290px;" valign="top">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="why-groupon-subtitle">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="why-groupon-subtitle">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="why-groupon-subtitle">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="why-groupon-subtitle">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="why-groupon-subtitle"><strong><span style="color: #000000;">An Exclusive Spotlight for Your Business</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #000000;">When you&rsquo;re the feature on ##SITE_NAME##, you are the star! We run no other features in your city for that day. It''s just you selling directly to an eager audience of thousands.</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="width: 10px;">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style="background-image: url(http://grouponpro.dev.agriya.com/img/theme-image/bg_why/bg-why4.png); width: 389px; height: 290px;" valign="top">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="why-groupon-subtitle">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="why-groupon-subtitle">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="why-groupon-subtitle">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="why-groupon-subtitle">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="why-groupon-subtitle"><strong><span style="color: #000000;">Big Exposure, Bigger Word of Mouth</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #000000;">A ##SITE_NAME## feature puts you in front of hundreds of thousands of subscribers nationwide &mdash; with thousands more opting in each day. Our subscribers share your offer with everyone they know via Facebook, Twi