INSERT INTO `setting_categories` (`id`, `created`, `modified`, `name`, `description`) VALUES
(1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Site', '<p>Here you can update the site related settings.</p>\r\n<p>You can update the informations like Site Name, Site Default City, Site Routing URL, Site Currency, Site language.</p>\r\n<p>You can also change the PayPal currency code here. To know more about PayPal supported currency codes visit <a target="_blank" href="https://cms.paypal.com/us/cgi-bin/?cmd=_render-content&content_ID=developer/e_howto_api_nvp_currency_codes">PayPal Currency Codes</a>'),
(2, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Meta', '<p>Meta element is used to provide information that is relevant to browsers or search engines like describing the content of your document.</p>\r\n'),
(3, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'User', '<p>Here you can update the user related settings.</p>\r\n'),
(7, '2009-05-29 22:01:55', '2009-05-29 22:01:55', 'Images', '<p>Here you can update the dimension (Height x Width) of the images.</p>\r\n'),
(8, '2009-05-29 22:01:55', '2009-05-29 22:01:55', 'Facebook', '<p>Here you can update facebook related settings. </p>\r\n<p>Facebook Application keys:</p>\r\n<p>Create Facebook Application by login to site <a href="http://www.facebook.com/developers/" target="_blank">http://www.facebook.com/developers/</a>.</p>\r\n<p>Facebook like button code:</p>\r\n<p>To get the Facebook like button code refer <a href="http://developers.facebook.com/docs/reference/plugins/like-box" target="_blank">http://developers.facebook.com/docs/reference/plugins/like-box</a>.</p>\r\n'),
(13, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Barcode', '<p>Here you can update the dimensions of barcode in deal coupon.</p>\r\n'),
(10, '2010-03-04 10:25:06', '2010-03-04 10:25:09', 'Wallet', '<p>Here you can update the minimum and maximum wallet amount.</p>\r\n'),
(11, '2010-03-04 10:25:23', '2010-03-04 10:25:26', 'Deal', '<p>Here you can update deal related settings.</p>\r\n'),
(12, '2010-03-25 18:10:06', '2010-03-25 18:10:06', 'Cash Withdraw', '<p>Here you can update minimum and maximum wallet amount of the user as well as company.</p>\r\n<p>For cash withdraw we require Masspay.</p>\r\n<p>You can update Masspay details in Paypal settings.</p>'),
(14, '2010-03-31 19:27:19', '2010-03-31 19:27:19', 'Friends', '<p>Here you can update the friends related settings.</p>\r\n<p> Create MSN application from the site <a href="http://dev.live.com/" target="_blank">http://dev.live.com/</a>.</p>\r\n<p> Create Yahoo application from the site <a href="http://developer.apps.yahoo.com/" target="_blank">http://developer.apps.yahoo.com/</a>.</p>\r\n'),
(15, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'User Privacy', '<p>Here you can update the user privacy related settings. </p>\r\n'),
(16, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Referral', '<p>Here you can update various referral system settings.</p>\r\n'),
(17, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Company', '<p>Here you can update company related settings. </p>\r\n'),
(18, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Twitter', '<p>You can change the twitter ''oAuth'' related settings here.</p><p> oAuth is used to post a message in twitter when a new deal coming to open status.</p><p> Refer, <a href="http://apiwiki.twitter.com/FAQ#WhenwillTwittersupportOAuth" target="_blank">http://apiwiki.twitter.com/FAQ#WhenwillTwittersupportOAuth</a> and <a href="http://apiwiki.twitter.com/FAQ#HowdoIget%E2%80%9CfromMyApp%E2%80%9DappendedtoupdatessentfrommyAPIapplication" target="_blank" >http://apiwiki.twitter.com/FAQ#HowdoIget%E2%80%9CfromMyApp%E2%80%9DappendedtoupdatessentfrommyAPIapplication</a>.</p>\r\n<p>We need to create a new application in twitter from <a href="http://twitter.com/apps/new" target="_blank">http://twitter.com/apps/new</a>.</p>\r\n<p>Update consumer key and consumer secret key here.</p>\r\n<p>Click Update Twitter Credentials and follow the steps.</p>\r\n<p>Once you finish, the access key and access token get automatically updated.</p>\r\n<p>To get Twitter widget code refer <a href="http://twitter.com/goodies/widgets" target="_blank">http://twitter.com/goodies/widgets</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n'),
(19, '2010-03-31 19:27:19', '2010-03-31 19:27:19', 'Email Template', '<p>Here you can update the email template related settings.</p>\r\n'),
(20, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Google Map', '<p>Here you can create Google map API from the site <a href="http://code.google.com/apis/maps/signup.html" target="_blank">http://code.google.com/apis/maps/signup.html</a>.</p>\r\n'),
(21, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'PayPal', '<p>Here you can update paypal related settings.</p>\r\n<p>Masspay used to sent money to user. </p>\r\n<p>Create masspay API from paypal profile. Refer <a href="https://www.paypal.com/in/cgi-bin/webscr" target="_blank">https://www.paypal.com/in/cgi-bin/webscr</a>.</p>\r\n<p>Direct pay allowed user to pay directly from credit card using capture authorization and void concept.it will let the user to pay only at the deal tipped state.</p>'),
(22, '2010-05-25 11:17:27', '2010-05-25 11:17:30', 'Bitly', '<p>Here you can update bitly related settings</p\r\n<p>Bitly allows to create short URLs.</p>\r\n<p>You need API key for this. Refer <a href="http://bit.ly/a/sign_in" target="_blank">http://bit.ly/a/sign_in</a>. </p>'),
(23, '2010-05-25 11:17:27', '2010-05-25 11:17:30', 'Gift Card', '<p>You can change the gift card related settings here.</p');
